    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Thermal storage walls consisting of south-facing, glass-fronted, thick masonry walls with circulation vents that pass heated air, stored during the day in the walls, into rooms during the night.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor muren met ruimteverwarming die bestaan uit dikke, gemetselde muren, gelegen op het zuiden en met een glazen gevel, waarin circulatiegaten zitten waaruit gedurende de nacht verwarmde lucht in de kamers komt die gedurende de dag in de muren is opgeslagen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>採朝南設計，表面為玻璃的厚重石造蓄熱牆，牆面在白天蓄集熱能，並於夜晚時將熱氣經由循環通道傳導至室內。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
